data.advs_desc:
Do You Have? Brief Summary

For A Strong Life

Recommendations from Dogan Djuceloglu…

I had a lot of tense, stressful, unhappy days in my youth. I've been through periods where I've felt guilty, thought I was worthless. Now my life is full of meaning, enthusiasm and a sense of gratitude... Why? Is it because of the improvement of the conditions in which I live? Is it the result of the awareness I have developed?

Doan Ccelolu

Dogan Djuceloglu is one of the most important scientists of this geography not only with his career in psychology, but also with his wisdom, which touches human life and can extract healing from every story about a person. As an accumulation of his more than eighty years of life, he now offers his most sincere answers to *vital* questions that everyone is wondering about. Like everyone else, in fact, he is still fighting, exploring, adding value to life.

What is the meaning of life?

How does a person develop himself?

How to overcome despair?
